HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 04:42:14 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 12-Aug-96 17:03:38 GMT
Content-length: 8316
Content-type: text/html
