<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/free/ST96/WolfIcon.ST1996.html 204.71.237.86 19970108044837 text/html 7930
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 04:48:52 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 15-Jul-96 14:00:58 GMT
Content-length: 7744
Content-type: text/html
