http://www.sbsc.org:80/free/ST96/Hooters.ST1996.html 204.71.237.86 19970108044917 text/html 7253
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 04:49:32 GMT
