governing, whatever you think of this President, whether you voted 
for him or not, he can hang -- which is to say he can do it...."
Arsenio Hall: "See! See! Dan is deep, ain't he? Dan in the 
Hood!...I thank you for being here. You're a special guy. And I 
hope whatever you have is contagious." -- Exchange from The 
Arsenio Hall Show, January 28.
