HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 05:07:41 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 07-Oct-96 21:42:17 GMT
Content-length: 8986
Content-type: text/html
