<DOCNO>WT16-B05-200</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000240-B017-110</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/mrc/cyberalert/cyb0911.html 204.71.237.86 19970108050923 text/html 11690
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 05:09:41 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 17-Sep-96 18:30:02 GMT
