http://www.sbsc.org:80/nationalreview/clinton/ramesh.html 204.71.237.86 19970108051312 text/html 11726
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 05:13:18 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 25-Nov-96 22:11:27 GMT
Content-length: 11539
Content-type: text/html
